<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="29Mar1927"><font color="red">29 March 1927</font> <i>BLHW</i> (to Harriet Weaver): I expect to arrive in London on Sunday evening. (3 April 1927) I shall stay at the Euston &hellip; I return to Paris on Wednesday (6 April 1927) &hellip; I shall be working here till the last moment. The typescript I sent you is not the final. </div>
